channel.title: Is it okay if
channel.description:
Is it okay if I release a bunch of Rsps related things in the Server Download Section all in one post? Ill list all of what I have, some of them are very uncommon now:
-Baranka [All 3] -Deathlypvpz V2 [All 3] -Project Rainbow [All 3] -Vistex V5 [All 3, includes original unbroken cache] -Solitude by LunarKnight [All 3] -TeamTorva [All 3] -Vistex V2 Client -Vistex V3 [All 3] -Frozen Wolf [Server Only, Compatible with TeamTorva Client+Cache] -InsidiaX V1 [All 3] -RS Font Generator -Acrylicx [All 3] -Custom Staff Capes -RS 2006 Remake [All 3+Im not sure what the name is, its similar to this, but Im too lazy to search it up] -Matrix 718 [Source+Client] -Abbyscape3 [All 3] -InsanityX Original Release by Gabbe [All 3 I believe] -syclonepk [All 3] -Lost Legacy by Omar/Playboy [All 3] -Delta Blank Source by RandQm [All 3] -Project Annihalation [All 3] -Vistex V7 [All 3] -TrisidiaX V3 [All 3] -teh pvserver custom p4ck v3
Im looking for more at the moment, and will put them here as I find them.
EDIT: HungerGames RSPS [All 3] Allstarscape [All 3] Mozilla317 [Solitude customized server, I've added a few zones, fixed a dupe or two, and added Announcements on Login and 99 in skill] [All 3] = Server+Client+Cache
P.S:Can I release these without permission? I havent been able to get hold of anyone from here other than Trisidia and the Vistex owner Omar/Stefano. P.P.S:If anyone wants these right now, simply add my skype: ali.abid331
